Package: scDHA
Type: Package
Title: single-cell Decomposition using Hierarchical Autoencoder 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Duc Tran, Hung Nguyen, Bang Tran, Carlo La Vecchia, Hung N. Luu and Tin Nguyen
Maintainer: Duc Tran <duct@nevada.unr.edu>
Description: Provide a fast and accurate pipeline for single-cell analyses. 
    The scDHA software package conducts cell segregation through unsupervised learning, dimension reduction and visualization, cell classification, and time-trajectory inference.
    scDHA currently supports macOS and Linux.
License: LGPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
Imports: matrixStats, foreach, keras, tensorflow, doParallel, igraph, Matrix, caret, cluster, clusterCrit, Rcpp, RcppParallel, RcppAnnoy, methods
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppParallel, RcppAnnoy
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
